# MVP scope guard

Source of truth:
- `docs/MVP-PLAN.md` — original MVP scope and flow
- `docs/VMS-FULL-COVERAGE-PLAN.md` — active VMS template expansion (Phase A/B/C + hardening track)

**Defer unless explicitly requested:**

- Candidate Supabase Auth / passwords
- Public open intake at `/` (invite links only)
- Virus scan, camera capture, duplicate detection
- Recruiter notes, candidate self-serve login

**Exception — in scope via epic #16 / VMS plan:** `/api/parse` rate limiting (issue #13).

**In scope:** invite-gated intake, parse + wizard, hospital search, DOCX export, admin hub, confirmation email (Resend), full VMS template coverage per `docs/VMS-FULL-COVERAGE-PLAN.md`.

If a request expands scope beyond the VMS plan, call it out and propose phased delivery (see `phase-labeling.mdc`).
